story-context.interfaces:
**RetryService Interface:**
```typescript
class RetryService {
  async executeWithRetry(
    operation: () => Promise,
    options?: {
      maxAttempts?: number;    // Default: 3
      baseDelay?: number;      // Default: 1000ms
      context?: string;        // For logging
      onRetry?: (attempt: number, error: Error) => void;
    }
  ): Promise
}
```

**IEmailProvider Interface:**
```typescript
interface IEmailProvider {
  send(to: string, subject: string, html: string, text?: string): Promise;
}

interface EmailResult {
  messageId: string;
  success: boolean;
}
```

**FonivaService Interface:**
```typescript
class FonivaService {
  sendSms(phoneNumber: string, message: string, type: SmsType, customId: string): Promise<{
    providerId: string;
  }>;
}
```

**ConfigService Usage:**
```typescript
// In constructor
this.mailRetryMaxAttempts = this.configService.get('MAIL_RETRY_MAX_ATTEMPTS', 5);
this.mailRetryBaseDelay = this.configService.get('MAIL_RETRY_BASE_DELAY', 2000);
this.smsRetryMaxAttempts = this.configService.get('SMS_RETRY_MAX_ATTEMPTS', 5);
this.smsRetryBaseDelay = this.configService.get('SMS_RETRY_BASE_DELAY', 2000);
```

**Retry Usage Pattern:**
```typescript
// MailService.sendEmail()
const result = await this.retryService.executeWithRetry(
  async () => await this.emailProvider.send(to, subject, html, text),
  {
    maxAttempts: this.mailRetryMaxAttempts,
    baseDelay: this.mailRetryBaseDelay,
    context: `Email Send: ${to} - ${subject}`
  }
);

// SMSService.sendSms()
const fonivaResult = await this.retryService.executeWithRetry(
  async () => await this.fonivaService.sendSms(phoneNumber, message, type, smsRecord.id),
  {
    maxAttempts: this.smsRetryMaxAttempts,
    baseDelay: this.smsRetryBaseDelay,
    context: `SMS Send: ${phoneNumber} - ${message.substring(0, 50)}...`
  }
);

// SMSService.retrySms() - REFACTORED
const fonivaResult = await this.retryService.executeWithRetry(
  async () => await this.fonivaService.sendSms(
    smsRecord.phoneNumber,
    smsRecord.message,
    smsRecord.type as SmsType,
    smsRecord.id
  ),
  {
    maxAttempts: 3 - smsRecord.attemptCount, // Remaining attempts
    baseDelay: this.smsRetryBaseDelay,
    context: `SMS Retry: ${smsRecord.id} (attempt ${smsRecord.attemptCount + 1}/3)`
  }
);
```
